Source: kitty
Section: x11
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl, xz-utils
Homepage: https://github.com/kovidgoyal/kitty

Package: kitty
Architecture: amd64
Description: The fast, feature-rich, GPU based terminal emulator.
 kitty is a fast, feature-rich, cross-platform, GPU based terminal emulator.
 It supports modern terminal features like graphics, ligatures, and true
 color, with a scriptable kitten framework for extending functionality.
